Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Conan Episode 1028 "Ballad \Nof the Woman Who Loved Cake"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,[OP]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:08.48,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,I'm absolutely certain. It's this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.86,0:00:16.12,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Just the thought of this mansion becoming \Na factory that makes tasty cakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:18.12,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\b1\fnTimes New Roman\bord3\shad0\fs17\pos(74,226)\blur2\3c&HACB3B0&\c&H3E433D&}Private Property\N{\c&H464270&}Do Not Enter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.29,0:00:20.37,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Is kind of exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:27.31,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,I want shortcake and mont blanc.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.31,0:00:30.39,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'd like \Ncheesecake and apple pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:37.04,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Then I want chocolate cake, \Nroll cake, pancakes, and flapjacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:39.80,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,You're being too greedy, Genta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:44.01,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.49,0:00:46.14,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, isn't that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.72,0:00:47.89,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Is that real?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:49.52,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.50,0:01:11.84,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\b1\fnTimes New Roman\bord3\shad0\fs14\blur2\3c&HACB3B0&\c&H3E433D&\move(155,200,155,324)}Private Property\N{\c&H464270&}Do Not Enter
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.03,0:01:12.67,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}This must be the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:28.34,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Finally arriving after \Nswaying back and forth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:30.06,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,draw close to mysteries and \Nbegin deducing the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.22,0:01:31.81,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The shadow of a woman moves \Nthrough a ruined building!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.81,0:01:33.69,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,In the air is the smell of \Nsomething sweet and a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.69,0:01:35.26,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Always determining the one truth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:37.12,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,with the body of a child \Nand the mind of an adult,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:39.93,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,his name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:17.96,DCEpTitle,EPTITLE,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(398,1)}Ballad of the Woman Who Loved Cake
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:15.54,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,"Ballad of the Woman Who Loved Cake!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.33,0:03:20.38,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourselves together, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.04,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.20,0:03:28.97,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What? A corpse came back to life?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:30.88,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:33.28,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-A hand reached out from beneath the debris!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.28,0:03:36.86,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,It started moving, and a \Nwoman wearing red emerged!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.01,0:03:44.74,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like that zombie is injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:47.99,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,If we follow this trail of blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:51.75,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll learn the true \Nidentity of that lady zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:55.25,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,How far does this trail go, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:58.75,Western Confections,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(363,1)\blur2}Western Confections
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:03:58.75,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Isn't this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:02.13,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Western Confections Paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.37,0:04:05.61,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Isn't that woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.26,0:04:09.38,DCItalic,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently there's a desolate \Nbuilding outside Haido City
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:12.77,DCItalic,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,where they're planning to establish \Na new factory for this bakery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:15.28,DCItalic,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,A desolate building? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:18.77,DCItalic,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,An old building no longer in use by anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:21.76,DCItalic,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds interesting. Let's check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:24.98,DCItalic,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have school next \NThursday, so let's go then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.98,0:04:26.91,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't do that if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:28.24,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.24,0:04:39.27,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The same woman is in the same seat \Neating the same cake as last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:41.09,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:46.17,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but she's wearing really dirty clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.17,0:04:47.25,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Those stains...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.25,0:04:50.06,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they a similar color to that debris?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:51.81,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:54.06,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,She's the lady zombie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.84,DCMain,EMPLOYEE,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.62,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Her ankle is injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:03.57,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotta be her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:12.86,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,The lady zombie is angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:13.89,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,After her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.65,0:05:16.29,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.91,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,She entered a building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.91,0:05:37.07,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,This is Western Confections \NParadise's main factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:37.35,Western Confections,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(177,87)\blur2}Western Confections
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:46.24,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord2\shad0\fs16\fnTimes New Roman\frz25.65\pos(202,97)\3c&H8B9190&\c&H2B3532&\blur2}President's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.24,0:05:47.49,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs20\bord2\shad0\fnArial\b1\3c&HBAB8B2&\c&H08060B&}Authorized Personnel Only\N{\c&H1D148A&}Do Not Enter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:50.71,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,The doorman will never let us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:51.86,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.67,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,We came this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:54.97,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:57.51,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:58.29,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord3\shad0\fnTimesNewRoman\fs26\3c&HA19993&\c&H1A1B10&\blur1\b1\pos(268,115)\fad(230,1)}Service Entrance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:13.03,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Yayoi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.03,0:06:14.72,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The president!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.04,0:06:21.10,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:31.93,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,C-Call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.93,0:06:35.82,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,And let everyone in the \Noffice know about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.05,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.64,0:06:40.04,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:40.91,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:48.76,DCItalic,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,This is my wife's handkerchief.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.19,DCItalic,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Could she have done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:57.48,DCMain,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:01.32,DCMain,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,What? The president's been murdered?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.32,0:07:02.77,DCMain,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,He drowned in red bean paste?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:05.76,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Anyway, where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.28,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I see. In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.89,0:07:12.41,DCMain,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,What? Let's have lunch at the apartment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.81,0:07:15.84,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Last night's leftover sukiyaki over rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:17.40,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:19.00,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:23.42,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord2\shad0\fnTimesNewRoman\fs22\c&HF2EAE4&\3c&H7B6B5E&\blur3\frz25.51\pos(247,93)}Call Ended
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:23.42,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord2\shad0\fnTimesNewRoman\fs22\c&HF2EAE4&\3c&H7B6B5E&\blur3\pos(267,128)\frz26.94}Ogawa Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:23.42,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\b1\fnTimesNewRoman\bord2\shad0\fs20\frz27.12\c&HE4EBD9&\3c&H5C41D1&\blur2\pos(303,248)}Block
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:23.42,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\b1\fnTimesNewRoman\bord2\shad0\fs20\frz27.12\c&HE4EBD9&\3c&H74A439&\blur2\pos(363,218)}Call Back
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.92,0:07:23.42,DCMain,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,He's creating an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.36,0:07:26.11,DCMain,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Could he have done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:28.95,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,This has turned into a serious situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:32.65,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think the lady zombie \Nis connected to the case?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:34.50,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:37.15,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,The Detective Boys are on the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:38.55,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,What? Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.55,0:07:40.92,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and gather information.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:41.65,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.46,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Conan, you watch the crime scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.46,0:07:44.40,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.90,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Boys, roll out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:47.90,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.65,0:07:55.16,Western Confections,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\move(203,208,245,208)\fs10}Western Confections
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:55.16,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,The deceased is Western Confections Paradise \Ncompany president Ogawa Akira-san, 35 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:58.90,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,He apparently suffocated \Nto death when his face
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:00.65,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,was pushed into a sink \Nfilled with red bean paste.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:03.13,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,What an eccentric murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:06.42,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Was the victim making a huge amount \Nof red bean soup or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:08.86,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Despite being the president of \Na Western confections factory,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.86,0:08:12.29,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,he apparently had become absorbed \Nin Japanese sweet-making recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:15.61,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine being killed by the red \Nbean paste you made yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:18.43,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:21.45,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd assist with the investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.97,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,since I'm already here to pick \Nup the kids as their guardian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:26.19,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,So, where's the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.91,0:08:29.44,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,He was around here until a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:32.87,DCMain,POLICE,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector, I've brought the \Npeople who discovered the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.12,0:08:39.08,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to trouble you when you're already \Ntired, but we have a few questions for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:42.87,DCNameCards,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(442,432)\pos(309,297)}Ogawa Hiroshi (29)\NWestern Confections Paradise VP
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:44.55,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You're the victim Ogawa Akira-san's younger \Nbrother and Vice President Ogawa Hiroshi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.55,0:08:48.09,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}and the president's secretary \NIto Yayoi-san, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:48.09,DCNameCards,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(316,1)\pos(285,297)\3c&HA87377&}Ito Yayoi (31)\NPresident's Secretary
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:51.52,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,The estimated time of death is 12PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.52,0:08:56.34,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that you're suspects, \Nbut where were you at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.62,0:09:00.60,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Around that time, I was crushed \Nbeneath some concrete.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:03.84,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What? C-Crushed beneath concrete?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:06.53,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,At the ruined building where we're \Nplanning to build our new factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.53,0:09:07.60,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Ruined building?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.98,0:09:10.28,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I was suppose to meet the president there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.14,0:09:13.49,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,We were going to elope.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.49,0:09:14.19,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.58,0:09:17.38,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,We were in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:22.42,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,But... no matter how long I waited, \Nthe president never showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:27.86,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I became overwhelmed by sadness \Nand went on a violent rampage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:31.76,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Then the concrete fell, \Ncrushing me beneath it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.73,0:09:38.11,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently I was unconscious for \Nsome time until I was awoken
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.11,0:09:40.52,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,by the dreadful voices of the Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:43.72,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Those children can attest \Nto what happened after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:46.83,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I should thank them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:51.56,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,So she knew we were following her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:54.23,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-san, what were you \Ndoing around that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.40,0:09:57.85,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,I returned to my apartment \Nto have lunch with my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:01.41,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,We had last night's leftover \Nsukiyaki over rice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.57,0:10:04.65,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:06.25,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.25,0:10:08.79,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of facts have come to light.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:14.87,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,The president was trying to develop Japanese \Nsweets to sell at Western Confections Paradise,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:18.80,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,but the VP was strongly opposed, \Nwhich caused friction between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.01,DCMain,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.39,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Hanako. Over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:26.21,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}So, that's the VP's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:26.89,DCNameCards,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(321,1)\pos(320,297)\3c&HA57668&}Ogawa Hanako (28)\NHiroshi's Wife
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.21,0:10:26.89,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:31.90,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,His wife sided with the VP and \Nalso opposed the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:35.62,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, where were you around 12PM today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:37.65,DCMain,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,I was at home with Hiroshi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.06,0:10:40.46,DCMain,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,We were eating beef bowls for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.46,0:10:43.66,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,She's matching her husband's \Nlie and fabricating an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:50.67,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The VP and his wife both think the other \Ndid it and are protecting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:54.16,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,The VP's wife is a rude lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:57.92,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,She bumped into me when she got out of \Nher red car at the bottom of the steps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.95,0:11:04.30,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,But she smelled nice, like she'd just gotten \Nout of the shower after shampooing her hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.69,0:11:07.40,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,A red car, shampoo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:10.31,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,I got a bunch of information, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:15.56,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the murdered president \Nplanned to convince the VP
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:19.57,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,and his wife who opposed him and build a \NJapanese sweets factory in that ruined building.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.76,0:11:22.64,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The ruined building, debris...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:27.79,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Ito-san, you seem to know a lot \Nabout the situation at your company
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:30.58,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,and the condition of your employees.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:31.57,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.57,0:11:37.38,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Though my title is the president's secretary, I'm \Nresponsible for taking care of the entire company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:40.97,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,She always assists us with the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:43.45,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,You know, that lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:45.60,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't a zombie at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:48.65,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she's an ordinary pretty lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:55.58,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, she said she was \Ngrateful your terrified voices woke her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:56.68,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:58.93,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:12:00.10,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,It was actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:01.49,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,The other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:02.72,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The other way around?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.72,0:12:05.02,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,She's not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.02,0:12:07.22,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,We did scream in terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:10.43,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,But it was because she came back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:14.68,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, tell me more about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:24.01,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, if you could \Nplease wait down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:27.13,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Confirm their alibis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:27.97,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:31.89,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, where did those kids go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:35.65,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,We need to discuss what \Nwe're going to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.78,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:40.70,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hold an emergency \Nmeeting in your office.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.70,0:12:42.44,DCMain,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.65,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,The sooner, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.93,0:12:48.97,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll come up with a good \Nsolution while eating something sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.01,0:13:00.30,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong with that kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.13,0:13:03.41,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:04.88,DCMain,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-san, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.10,0:13:14.35,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.15,0:13:17.10,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Your wife didn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.32,0:13:22.32,DCMain,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord3\shad0\fnTimesNewRoman\fs25\blur2\3c&HD0D1D3&\c&H181515&\b1\move(241,54,315,54)}Vice President's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.52,0:13:25.88,DCMain,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi-san, what was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:30.08,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently some kids had entered the woods,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.46,0:13:32.30,DCMain,HIROSHI,0000,0000,0000,,but I couldn't find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.30,0:13:35.83,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably the Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:39.71,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I need to contact someone \Nregarding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:42.01,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,You two go ahead and eat without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.01,0:13:43.56,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.53,0:13:49.39,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that kid go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:51.03,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:52.76,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.85,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,It's just you kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:56.08,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Where's four-eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.69,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,He went that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:59.40,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,That way? All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:02.06,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wander around too much, kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:02.90,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:05.04,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Detective Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:09.00,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun?! Mori-san's been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.00,0:14:10.10,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.10,0:14:15.03,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, he said he wanted forensics \Nto look into something for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.03,0:14:15.83,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:19.93,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:45.68,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do the Detective Boys like cake as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:46.70,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:47.61,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.84,0:14:50.63,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoy cake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.14,0:14:53.80,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, I love it dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:57.00,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't thanked you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:58.44,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,Thanked us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.44,0:15:05.20,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,For testifying that you found me crushed \Nbeneath concrete in the ruined building.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:08.28,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Detective Boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:14.01,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I sensed you fearfully entering \Nthe ruined building then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.43,0:15:20.40,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,We were laughing then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:25.41,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Then a woman came back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:29.61,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.09,0:15:35.28,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,You used the Detective Boys \Nto fabricate an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.04,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.96,0:15:39.40,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:40.83,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:43.30,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:49.76,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you wandering around the crime \Nscene like some little wandering...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.71,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! He's so heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:57.76,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,This case is the sad ballad \Nof a woman who loves cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:16:01.28,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,The sad ballad of a woman who loves cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.28,0:16:02.96,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,What is this old dude talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.96,0:16:05.77,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, where is his voice coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:09.28,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to what I have to say \Nas we dance a waltz together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:10.53,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.33,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,They're...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:16.78,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,...dancing a waltz.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.11,0:16:23.16,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,This ballad began one week ago at the Western \NConfections Paradise cake shop in Haido City,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.54,0:16:29.41,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,when the woman who loves cake learned of the \NDetective Boys' plan to explore a ruined building.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.20,0:16:34.88,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,This morning, the woman who loves \Ncake went to said ruined building.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:37.90,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Using a long thread and plywood boards,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:41.42,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,she rigged some debris to fall automatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:46.19,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Conan found signs of this contrivance \Nin the ruined structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:49.94,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,On the path between the ruined building \Nand Western Confections Paradise,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.21,0:16:55.45,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,she left a trail of blood beforehand \Nso the Detective Boys would follow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.21,0:17:00.70,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,She returned to the office and waited for \Nthe right moment to speak to the VP's wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.14,DCItalic,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:06.25,DCItalic,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,The president forgot some documents \Nat the new factory site.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.25,0:17:07.35,DCItalic,HANAKO,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:12.92,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The VP's wife headed to the \Nruined building in a red car,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.47,0:17:17.64,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,where she triggered the tripwire \Nand was crushed beneath the debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.15,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.47,0:17:26.16,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Awoken by the laughter of the \NDetective Boys who had arrived,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.16,0:17:30.74,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,she failed to notice their presence \Nand hastily left out of fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.74,0:17:36.92,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,At that time, Conan saw a red \Ncar driving down the hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:41.72,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Since the VP's wife didn't return to \Nthe office until after the murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:45.55,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,she must've returned home and taken a shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:48.83,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the woman who loves cake
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:52.02,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,headed to the president's office \Nas though nothing had happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.95,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,She waited for an opportunity \Nto kill the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:18:02.51,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,left behind the VP's wife's handkerchief \Nshe'd stolen beforehand, and left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:06.56,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The VP and his wife suspected each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:12.21,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,The lies they told ultimately fabricated \Nan alibi for the woman who loves cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.21,0:18:14.23,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,For the woman who loves cake,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:19.26,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,predicting the VP and his wife's actions \Nand manipulating them was a simple task.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.91,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she's the secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:24.44,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,Then the woman who loves cake waited.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.88,0:18:29.42,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,She wore clothes similar to the VP's \Nwife, stained her ankle with blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.91,0:18:32.00,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,and ate cake while she waited,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:35.32,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,as though waiting for a lover,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.41,0:18:38.94,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,for the Detective Boys to follow the trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.88,0:18:46.19,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how the Detective Boys \Nwere used to fabricate an alibi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:47.77,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,for the sad woman who loves cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:51.16,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:54.20,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,What proof is there that \NI killed the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:58.07,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,This is all just the nonsensical reasoning \Nof an old dude who reeks of cigarettes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.74,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. There's no evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:01.99,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,See? Told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:05.49,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,But what about the VP and \Nhis wife's testimony?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:07.12,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:12.00,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What makes the woman who loves cake say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:12.78,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.78,0:19:14.06,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,On what basis do you make that claim?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:17.63,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,What basis? None, it's just what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.85,0:19:19.38,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,No, there is something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.53,0:19:21.89,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,This old dude who reeks of cigarettes knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.13,0:19:23.64,DCMain,ALL,0000,0000,0000,,He admitted it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.64,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,What are you claiming to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:30.64,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,I know the woman who loves cake poisoned \Nthe VP and his wife and tried to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:33.15,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.70,0:19:35.45,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Now you've said it! How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.45,0:19:36.40,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.21,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:41.40,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,A murderer has no right \Nto speak to me that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.41,0:19:45.41,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,But don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:46.50,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:49.33,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,What do you see on the \Nother side of that glass?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.16,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,The glass? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.13,0:19:58.68,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,B-But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:01.09,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I told them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.39,0:20:03.80,DCItalic,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit is the secretary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:10.10,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,I had them pretend to be poisoned \Nwithout eating the matcha cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.36,0:20:14.60,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,The police told me earlier that \Nthey found poison in the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.95,0:20:23.06,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the ballad of \Nthe woman who loves cake
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:26.18,DCMain,KOGORO,0000,0000,0000,,ended with her betrayal \Nby the cake she loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:34.62,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't forgive the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.60,0:20:41.13,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,How could my beloved Western Confections \NParadise make Japanese sweets of all things?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.65,0:20:43.68,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,At first, they opposed the idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.68,0:20:48.18,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,but the VP and his wife were just as guilty \Nfor accepting the president's suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:53.64,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Western Confections Paradise was my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:57.10,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,And my precious Western Confections Paradise
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.10,0:21:01.15,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,needed to be a paradise of Western \Nconfections, true to its name.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:05.37,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Shortcake, mont blanc, cheesecake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:07.92,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved Western sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.56,0:21:12.26,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Apple pie, chocolate cake, Ã©clairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:16.18,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,A paradise of Western sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:20.38,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,We heard everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:21.71,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Ito Yayoi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.01,0:21:27.36,DCMain,TAKAGI,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell us more about that elsewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.85,0:21:28.91,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Ito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.42,0:21:31.81,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Cream puff and maritozzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.62,0:21:33.96,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Shortcake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:38.76,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Cheesecake, apple pie, chocolate cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.32,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Mont blanc, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.59,0:21:42.68,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Ito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.68,0:21:45.13,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,Ito Yayoi-san, is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.13,0:21:46.71,DCMain,MEGURE,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.40,0:21:48.32,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.06,0:21:50.24,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:59.00,DCMain,YAYOI,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1101)}I wanted to create a true \Nparadise of Western sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.86,0:23:30.31,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,So they're making a Japanese sweets \Nfactory instead of a cake factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.09,0:23:32.47,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Daifuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:33.90,DCMain,MITSUHIKO,0000,0000,0000,,Dorayaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.90,0:23:35.16,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Kintsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.16,0:23:36.47,DCMain,CONAN,0000,0000,0000,,Amanatto.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.76,0:23:38.17,DCMain,GENTA,0000,0000,0000,,Potato yokan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.17,0:23:39.63,DCMain,MITSUIHKO,0000,0000,0000,,Soft yokan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.63,0:23:41.16,DCMain,AYUMI,0000,0000,0000,,Steamed yokan.
